title: Golden Horn wins Prix de l'Arc de Triomphe
text:
> Sports Golden Horn wins Prix de l'Arc de Triomphe Italian jockey Frankie Dettori reacts after winning the Qatar Prix de l'Arc de Triomphe horse race, riding Golden Horn, at the Longchamp horse racetrack, outside Paris, Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015. (AP Photo/Kamil Zihnioglu)
